      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S RX-7 is a masterclass in 90s JDM engineering, featuring the legendary 13B-REW twin-rotor engine with a seamless sequential twin-turbo transition. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise five-speed manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The chassis retains its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension with all-aluminum control arms, preserving the celebrated 50/50 weight distribution. Meticulously maintained with verified compression across all rotor faces and a pristine vacuum system, this vehicle represents a rare, mechanically unmolested example of the 'Spirit R' era performance.",
